    public abstract class ConstDecl<DeclType extends Type>
extends Decl<DeclType>
    Abstract base class for constants. Use BasicConstDecl for a basic constant, or IndexedConstDecl if the constant belongs to a variable for some index (e.g., during unfolding paths).
